<font size="2" color="#003366"><b>International CES - The World's Largest Annual Technology Tradeshow</b></font><p>

With the new expansion of the Las Vegas Convention Center, the 2002 CES will have room to host exhibitors all 
under one roof, making it easier for attendees to see the entire show. More than 1,040 companies have signed 
up for more than 1.1 million square feet of 2002 CES exhibit space. The show floor will be filled with the 
most exciting technologies in consumer electronics.
<br>
<p>

<font size="2" color="#003366"><b>2001 CES Highlights Digital Technology</b></font><br><br>

More than 122,000 industry professionals from 120 countries came to Las Vegas to see the cutting edge in 
digital technology at the 2001 International CES, featuring four days of conference sessions, keynote 
speeches and exhibits of consumer technology. 
<p>
To view the <b>2001 CES Keynote Speeches</b> from Craig R. Barrett, Bill Gates, Carl Yankowski and Barry Schuler,
<a href="http://www.cesweb.org/press/show_news.asp">Click Here</a>.
<p>

